SEARCH
Module com.jp.passwordmanager
Package passwordmanager.database

Class SearchResultsCache

java.lang.Object
passwordmanager.model.SearchResultNodesCache
public class SearchResultsCache extends Object
The SearchResultsCache class is a singleton that provides a cache for search result nodes in the password manager application. This class retrieves all entries from the EntryCache and generates their corresponding FXML nodes for displaying search results. It also provides methods to access the cached search result nodes.

This class ensures that the search result nodes are generated efficiently, and provides timing information for this operation.

Usage example: 

 
 SearchResultsCache cache = SearchResultsCache.getInstance();
 ArrayList<Node> searchResultsNodes = cache.getSearchResultsNodes();
